IBM Maximo Application Suite v8.11.23¤

Release Notes¤

Bug Fixes and Security Updates¤

  • Fix for Labels & update of Graphite to v2.12.423 for MAS811 Navigator-App (#3732)
  • Update coreapi image to get new changes for passwordpolicy (#3766)
  • Added CRD changes for IDP status change API (#3740)
  • Fix SAML race condition (#3775)
  • Add qualtrics to the Suite CRD to avoid having the property removed from the CRD in a cluster where a 9.1 instance is installed - 811x (#3737)
  • set liberty version 25.0.0.2 into coreidp: 811x (#3793)
  • Fix for Labels & update of Graphite to v2.12.432 for MAS811 Navigator-App (#3802)
  • Add 811x prev release into rollback supported images list (811x) (#3842)
